---
title: Fleury
permalink: 'index/{{ index.url | slugify }}/'
layout: layout.njk
csspath: ./css/
---

<header class="header">
	<h1><img width="58px" src="../../images/2/fleury.png" alt=""><br>{{ title }}</h1>
	<nav class="header___nav">
		<ul>
			<li><a href="../../index">HOME</a></li>
			<li><a href="../photo">ABOUT</a></li>
			<li><img width="15" src="../../images/2/cart_icon.png" alt=""></li>
		</ul>
	</nav>
</header>

<main class="main">

	<div class="main___header">
		<h2>多重露光した、写真です。<br>
		<span class="h2___sm">This is a multiple exposure photo.</span></h2>
		<img width="1020" src="../../images/scenery10.jpg" alt="">
	</div>

	<div class="main___main">
		<div class="about">
			<div class="about___block">
				<h3>ABOUT</h3>
				<p class="fl">Fleuryとは？</p>
				<p class="txt">Fleuryは、景色との重ねた写真を売っているショップです。<br>
				花 fleurと景色 sceneryを掛け合わせた名前にしました。</p>
				<p class="and more">and more....</p>
			</div>
		</div>

	<h3>PRODUCTS</h3>
	<p>取り扱い商品</p>
	<!-- 各sectionをループで作成 -->
	<div class="product___photo">
		{% for product in products %}
		<section class="{{ product.url }}">
			<div class="photo___img">
				<img width="500" src="../../images/{{ product.itemphotos[0] }}" alt="{{ product.name }}" />
				<h4>{{ product.name }}</h4>
				<p>¥{{ product.price }}</p>
				<button class="btn">{{ product.state }}</button>
			</div>
		</section>
		{% endfor %}
	</div>
		<p class="view more">VIEW MORE</p>
	</div>
</main>
<footer class="footer">
	<h4><img width="58px" src="../../images/2/fleury.png" alt="">Fleury</h4>
	<div class="copyright">
		<small>©︎2022 Fleury Ltd.</small>
	</div>
</footer>


